title: Vegans: Beyond Abolitionism (Beyond PETA & Peter Singer, too)
description:
Support the creation of this content (for just $1 per month) on Patreon, here: https://www.patreon.com/a_bas_le_ciel
Check out ModVegan's channel, here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCXwREs2xdJSI0Zj9nL2MzKA/videos

As mentioned in the intro, you can see photographs of my (very photogenic) life in China if you find me on "Nice" (OneNiceApp)… this is basically a competitor to Instagram.  Some people have said that it's easier to find me if you search for my Chinese name (马大影, ma-da-ying) within the app. www.oneniceapp.com

The book discussed throughout this video is by Gary L. Francione & Anna Charlton, 2015, titled, "Animal Rights: The Abolitionist Approach".
